|<span data-ttu-id="55af0-109">Element</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="55af0-109">Item</span></span>|`DisplayAttributes`|  
|----------|-------------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="55af0-110">Hallo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="55af0-110">Hello</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="55af0-111">Onetrailingspace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="55af0-111">OneTrailingSpace</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="55af0-112">,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="55af0-112">,</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="55af0-113">Onetrailingspace &#124; consumeleadingspaces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="55af0-113">OneTrailingSpace &#124; ConsumeLeadingSpaces</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="55af0-114">he</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="55af0-114">he</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="55af0-115">Onetrailingspace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="55af0-115">OneTrailingSpace</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="55af0-116">hat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="55af0-116">said</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="55af0-117">Onetrailingspace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="55af0-117">OneTrailingSpace</span></span>|  
